---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="About" description="Floof is a fun, young, vibrant clothing brand from Southwest Florida.">
  <section class="bg-floof-dark text-white py-16"><div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center"><h1 class="text-4xl font-bold md:text-5xl">About <span class="text-floof-gradient">Floof</span></h1><p class="mt-4 text-white/60">Where the Gulf breeze meets good vibes.</p></div></section>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 space-y-12">
    <div><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">The Short Version</h2><p class="mt-4 text-floof-dark/70 leading-relaxed">Floof started with a simple observation: Southwest Florida has a vibe unlike anywhere else, but most of the merch out there is generic palm tree prints. We wanted something different — clothes that capture the energy of living where the sun shines 250+ days a year.</p></div>
    <div><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">What's With the Name?</h2><p class="mt-4 text-floof-dark/70 leading-relaxed">Floof is the sound a beach umbrella makes when the wind catches it. It's the feeling of sand between your toes. It's that perfect sunset moment when you think, "Yeah, this is why I live here." Unserious by design.</p></div>
    <div class="text-center pt-8"><a href="/store" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-floof-pink px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-floof-coral">Shop the Collection</a></div>
  </div>
</Layout>